snippet.title: Reader Rabbit Thinking Adventures Ages 4-6 Part 1/4 - Painting wrapping papers and banners
snippet.description:
Recorded on my birthday; 30th March.

It's Sam's birthday. Reader Rabbit and his friends need your help to get everything prepared for the birthday party.

In this episode, Reader Rabbit visits Pierre in his art studio. He is a majestic artist on painting patterned wrapping paper and making banner cards with different shapes, colors and patterns.
